summary:
Passionate and dedicated to the wellbeing and growth of all individuals, I seek to promote respectful and supportive relationships in or outside of the workplace. I have found my purpose in building inclusive communities, creating engaging initiatives which focus on the creation of connection, people wellbeing as well as help them develop a personal sense of development and accomplishment. 
I aim to always offer a safe and open environment where all belong. I thrive in situations which require problem solving skills, independence, interpersonal skills and creativity.
